Rules:
Damage Guide.

Raider               |   3–8 = Destroyed
Heavy Raider    |   7–8 = Destroyed
Viper                 |   5–7 = Damaged   8 = Destroyed
Civilian Ship     |   Automatically Destroyed  (no die roll)
Galactica          |   With Raider: 8 = Damaged
                         |   With Basestar: 4–8 = Damaged
Basestar           |   With Viper: 8 = Damaged
                         |   With Galactica: 5–8 = Damaged
                         |   With Nuke: 1–2 = Damaged Twice
                         |   3–6 = Destroyed
                         |   7–8 = Basestar and 3 Raiders Destroyed

First thing to do is to choose which expansions to use.

After deciding on which expansions to use you'll want to delete the extra boards, items on the boards that you delete, and character plates associated with that expansion.

Each board and the location cards on the boards are locked and can only be removed by right-clicking them, then deleting.

Next step is to choose a Destination and delete objects associated with destinations not chosen.

Next determine character selection
